				                <div><p>Thanks for the reply, JeffMa. &nbsp;But, again: &nbsp;I don't understand how any of your suggestions here (in your reply to my post) would help. &nbsp;The web server still has to respond to each and every request from a client, whether it's to reject the direct POST, reject based on the IP address, or deliver a 404. &nbsp;</p>
